ck\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ila1665702671184.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ila1665702671184.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ila1665702671184.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ila1665702671184\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ila1665702671184___application__470550\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set\n      application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ila1665702671184__p_d144356e1_d144357e1_d144358e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nlogotime=3\nlogosynch=off</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ila1665702671184__topic_d103402e1_d103403e1_d103404e1_d103405e1_d103406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1106816e58\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ila1665702671184__p_d144362e1_d144363e1_d144364e1\">The settings <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Shell</span>,\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Window</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DefEntity</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Menu</span> and\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Panel</span> enable you to set default widget properties for the\n            application shell, form windows, default entity widget, menus, and panels. Depending on\n            the object, these properties may be overridden at runtime properties set declaratively\n            or in script.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ila1665702671184__p_d144365e1_d144366e1_d144367e1\">Other settings in the section enable you to display a logo when the application is started and control the length of time widget tooltips are displayed.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xeu1665702671037.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>usys.ini</a><p>The usys.ini file is the default initialization file for Uniface applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uef1704698451038.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Properties for Styling the User Interface</a><p>Each object that can be viewed in the user interface has a collection of properties that can be used to control what it looks like, and some other aspects of its visual behavior.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wba1704709264749.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Setting Widget Properties in the Properties Inspector</a><p>Properties that are set in the Properties Inspector override the default property values set for the widget (if applicable) in the initialization file. At runtime, these properties may be overridden by properties set in script.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/szv1704710657865.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Setting Properties in Script</a><p>You can dynamically set widget properties at runtime using ProcScript, or for dynamic server pages, in JavaScript.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528595\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528595\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[application] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application. For example: [application] logotime=3 logosynch=off Copy Description The settings Shell , Window , DefEntity , Menu and Panel enable you to set default widget properties for the application shell, form windows, default entity widget, menus, and panels. Depending on the object, these properties may be overridden at runtime properties set declaratively or in script. Other settings in the section enable you to display a logo when the application is started and control the length of time widget tooltips are displayed. Related Links usys.ini The usys.ini file is the default initialization file for Uniface applications. Properties for Styling the User Interface Each object that can be viewed in the user interface has a collection of properties that can be used to control what it looks like, and some other aspects of its visual behavior. Setting Widget Properties in the Properties Inspector Properties that are set in the Properties Inspector override the default property values set for the widget (if applicable) in the initialization file. At runtime, these properties may be overridden by properties set in script. Setting Properties in Script You can dynamically set widget properties at runtime using ProcScript, or for dynamic server pages, in JavaScript. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}